summary:
Quantitative Finance Masters graduate from UvA.  BSocSci graduate in Economics and Political and International Studies from Rhodes University (South Africa). Former SEFA Master Career Club : Finance chairperson and English teacher in South Korea. Interested in Finance, Economics and Politics (most notably US politics).

For more information please email me at lukeroux@yahoo.com
